desc: Kanaka Māoli Owned and Operated business creating energy healing products from Ko’olaupoko, Kailua, ‘Oahu

layout.text: Aloha! My name is Brandi and I am the owner of Ka Pūnana Meli, we are a family owned and operated Kanaka Business. Here you will find all things that are Pono and in alignment with Spiritual Energy Healing, 10% of our income is used to support Kanaka Maoli organizations. Feel free to browse and if you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.
